1
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,960
[Episode 8: Be Braver Later]

2
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,840
Run! It's raining!

3
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,152
Hurry!

4
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:38,091
You said you didn't take it home.

5
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:44,200
I didn't.

6
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,359
I just... hid it here.

7
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:48,127
Isn't it boring?

8
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,159
Back then,

9
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:55,800
the neighborhood kids
played hide-and-seek here.

10
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,400
A boy

11
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:59,760
always tagged before counting to 100.

12
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,447
I'm hard of hearing.

13
00:02:01,447 --> 00:02:04,080
I thought it was
because I couldn't hear clearly

14
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:06,439
that I was caught before hiding safely.

15
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,951
The caught would be it.

16
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:09,719
I feared

17
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:11,480
no one would play with me.

18
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:14,039
So I had to remain

19
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,632
as it.

20
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:17,840
Then

21
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,770
a girl came over.

22
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,850
And then?

23
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:24,440
When she was it,

24
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,400
I hid here.

25
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,599
Later,

26
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:29,570
she found everyone else

27
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,009
except me.

28
00:02:32,759 --> 00:02:35,280
I hid her belongings here

29
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,836
to know

30
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,879
if she fooled me on purpose

31
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:40,360
like everyone else did,

32
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,599
or if she really

33
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:44,465
couldn't find me.

34
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:50,043
We knew each other so early.

35
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:53,460
I observed you from afar.

36
00:02:58,370 --> 00:02:59,700
[Certificate of Honor]

37
00:03:06,887 --> 00:03:08,826
Why didn't you tell me?

38
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:12,406
I told you in my letters.

39
00:03:12,406 --> 00:03:14,014
You never replied.

40
00:03:16,815 --> 00:03:19,520
You went to such a good university abroad.

41
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:22,052
It's normal if you had no time to read them.

42
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,039
Because I was a bad woman

43
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,672
who abandoned her boyfriend

44
00:03:29,672 --> 00:03:31,120
at the downturn of his career

45
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,919
for a bright future and

46
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:34,286
high salaries.

47
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,479
I even fantasized

48
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:40,280
that you had a terminal illness

49
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,959
and didn't want to be my burden.

50
00:03:42,858 --> 00:03:44,480
You deserve to be a famous scriptwriter.

51
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,540
Famous scriptwriter?

52
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:47,026
Yes.

53
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:50,159
When I worked in the CBD,

54
00:03:50,159 --> 00:03:51,960
the pantry had a window

55
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,800
facing the large screen in the square.

56
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,240
It advertised new series

57
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,439
at least three times daily.

58
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:59,000
And you were credited

59
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,960
as the scriptwriter,

60
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,284
in a huge and annoying font.

61
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:06,319
A disgusting colleague told me

62
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:09,220
you were a famous and outstanding scriptwriter.

63
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:12,200
So I was reluctant to drink water

64
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:14,081
and got pharyngitis.

65
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:17,082
- My fault?
- My fault.

66
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:20,480
I was vain, pretentious,

67
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,920
shabby-genteel,

68
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,279
longed for a decent life,

69
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:26,680
a decent job,

70
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,280
a fortune,

71
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,560
a big house,

72
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,997
traveling around,

73
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,399
flaunting on social media,

74
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:34,399
"See?"

75
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:36,720
"That's how cool I am."

76
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:39,075
Like the bird you hate.

77
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,896
Congrats. You made it.

78
00:04:46,119 --> 00:04:47,960
You must make a lot of money.

79
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,669
Why are you still living here?

80
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,319
A simple life is best.

81
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,560
Look,

82
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,519
we're so different.

83
00:04:57,519 --> 00:04:59,504
Our breakup is only a matter of time.

84
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:02,720
It's better to make friends
than to make enemies.

85
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,879
Compared to disconnection,

86
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:06,911
isn't friendship better?

87
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,410
Hang up if you don't want to answer.

88
00:05:13,410 --> 00:05:15,399
Answer it if you want to.

89
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:17,603
I don't want to embarrass us when we meet.

90
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:23,204
[Dude, help! I'll credit you next time
when we sign a contract.]

91
00:05:23,204 --> 00:05:25,245
No need to meet such a person.

92
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,651
<i>Hello, Nan Feng. I mean...</i>

93
00:05:27,651 --> 00:05:28,879
Have some shame.

94
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:30,720
No credit. No contract.

95
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:33,040
You want Mr. Xiang to work for you for free?

96
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,360
<i>My kid is sick! I...</i>

97
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,920
Are you taking care of your kid
in the hospital?

98
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:39,400
If not, why are you trying to gain sympathy?

99
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,683
Get lost!

100
00:05:40,683 --> 00:05:42,590
<i>- No, who are you?</i>
- None of your business!

101
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:43,715
<i>I...</i>

102
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,000
Aggressive with me,

103
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,250
but cowardly with others?

104
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,080
Mr. Xiang,

105
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,820
didn't you get it backwards?

106
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,160
The rain stopped.

107
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,429
Let's go.

108
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,841
Be braver later.

109
00:06:57,099 --> 00:06:58,983
Didn't we make

110
00:06:58,983 --> 00:07:01,240
the mackerel sauce together?

111
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,378
<i>So? Can't I use it?</i>

112
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,120
Forget it.

113
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,012
At least you're willing to teach her.

114
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:11,480
<i>Your daughter
rendered lard for me for three days.</i>

115
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,242
<i>It's a reward.</i>

116
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,926
It's delicious.

117
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:22,319
<i>You call me at midnight</i>

118
00:07:22,319 --> 00:07:23,921
<i>just to say this?</i>

119
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,240
I'm hanging up.

120
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,372
<i>Okay.</i>

121
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:39,199
These are the meal expenses I covered

122
00:07:39,199 --> 00:07:42,480
for the department over the past three years,

123
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:47,200
for each of you,

124
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:49,319
meal expenses,

125
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:51,439
transportation fares,

126
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:53,250
online shopping expenses,

127
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:54,519
etc.

128
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:56,040
The screenshots,

129
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:58,759
invoices and chat records

130
00:07:58,759 --> 00:08:02,519
of each payment

131
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:05,839
are attached

132
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:09,965
as the evidence.

133
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,365
Pay me back.

134
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,839
<i>Aggressive with me,</i>

135
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:20,160
<i>but cowardly with others?</i>

136
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,600
<i>Mr. Xiang,</i>

137
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,432
<i>didn't you get it backwards?</i>

138
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,907
<i>Be braver later.</i>

139
00:08:26,698 --> 00:08:29,420
It takes courage to be frank.

140
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,800
First, write the flyer yourself.

141
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:35,120
Second, pay and credit me as I deserve.

142
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,200
Third,

143
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,964
you are not my friend.

144
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,780
For you, as a gift.

145
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,119
What?

146
00:08:45,119 --> 00:08:46,680
Li Nan Xi told me

147
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,996
you wanted this jellyfish hairpin.

148
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:53,399
I... I saved up my own money to buy it.

149
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:55,279
I... and Zhao Xin

150
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:58,120
are also robbed by him.

151
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,399
But fearing his fists,

152
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:02,559
we only dare to tip the targeted

153
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:03,824
students off.

154
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,600
What about Xiang Nan Feng?

155
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,600
I tried to stop,

156
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,372
but failed.

157
00:09:11,377 --> 00:09:12,559
Thank you.

158
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:14,360
If you hadn't stood up for me,

159
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:17,048
I might still be Wang Chao Ran's friend.

160
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,120
A friend

161
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,360
never extorts

162
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,000
or requires expensive gifts

163
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,600
for a favor.

164
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,060
Besides,

165
00:09:28,060 --> 00:09:29,949
I hate owing someone a favor.

166
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,222
We're friends?

167
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,672
You covered for me,

168
00:09:40,672 --> 00:09:42,760
though failed.

169
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,679
May I ask you a question?

170
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:45,879
Go ahead if you want.

171
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:47,399
Why the permission?

172
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:49,120
So what if you don't get it?

173
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:50,480
People might be annoyed.

174
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,799
So what if they're annoyed?

175
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:52,919
I don't want to be disliked.

176
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:54,159
So what if you're disliked?

177
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:55,580
Will you die?

178
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,480
No.

179
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,919
Just do what you like.

180
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:01,054
Why do you care if others like...

181
00:10:01,054 --> 00:10:03,045
<i>I don't like black-crowned night herons.</i>

182
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,159
<i>They're pretentious,</i>

183
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:06,815
<i>utterly hypocritical.</i>

184
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,680
Why do you care if others like or not?

185
00:10:11,680 --> 00:10:13,142
Thank you.

186
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:19,200
How long will you squat?

187
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,160
I...

188
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:27,017
I heard nothing.

189
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,421
Wipe that off.

190
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:57,000
Didn't you say

191
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,280
you hate owing favors?

192
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,879
Didn't you say you heard nothing?

193
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:03,261
Ren Xi Zhou! After school tomorrow...

194
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:06,280
After school tomorrow, can we...

195
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:08,594
[On Duty: Ren Xi Zhou]
walk home together?

196
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:23,160
I'm sorry. The streetlights are dim.

197
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,454
I can't see clearly.

198
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,889
You can take off your sunglasses.

199
00:11:27,889 --> 00:11:29,197
Oh, yes.

200
00:11:30,565 --> 00:11:32,125
Xiang Nan Feng?

201
00:11:32,798 --> 00:11:33,880
Mr. Xiang!

202
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:35,039
You're...

203
00:11:35,039 --> 00:11:36,039
Me!

204
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:38,463
Zhu Qiao Fei! I sat behind you in high school.

205
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,879
Why are you back too?

206
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:42,200
Actually...

207
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,959
I come for someone.

208
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,800
<i>I've paid you back.</i>

209
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,805
<i>Where's your client list?</i>

210
00:12:06,805 --> 00:12:08,080
<i>Send me a copy.</i>

211
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,480
Let me check.

212
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,000
It might take a while.

213
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,671
Wait.

214
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:19,149
<i>Don't be too late.</i>

215
00:12:19,149 --> 00:12:20,320
<i>I have an early shift tomorrow.</i>

216
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,151
"Early shift tomorrow."

217
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:45,832
<i>Are you done?</i>

218
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,360
Not yet.

219
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,919
I was just messing with you.

220
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:52,000
Did you learn

221
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:54,359
to be shameless from Zhao Qi Ming?

222
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:04,254
How dare you block me?

223
00:13:09,724 --> 00:13:10,920
Ren Xi Zhou!

224
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:12,340
Get to work!

225
00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:13,640
Oh.

226
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:15,024
Coming!

227
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,600
Shabby washing machine.

228
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,139
It broke down suddenly.

229
00:13:23,759 --> 00:13:26,240
Being used for so long, it should break down.

230
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:28,298
Even if fixed, it'll only last a while.

231
00:13:28,298 --> 00:13:30,450
Why not spend more and buy a better one?

232
00:13:30,450 --> 00:13:32,892
Good things don't come cheap.

233
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:39,194
[Recycler]
[Top Cutie: Please remember to get the package]

234
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,360
<i>Hello,</i>

235
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,920
<i>I'm a student.</i>

236
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:47,159
<i>I'm sincere. Can I get a discount?</i>

237
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:49,262
<i>Self-pickup is acceptable.</i>

238
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,685
Hello, Mr. Xiang.

239
00:13:53,685 --> 00:13:56,602
Could you spare time
to help me move a washing machine?

240
00:14:00,601 --> 00:14:03,474
Hello? I come for the washing machine.

241
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:09,000
Li Nan Xi?

242
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,056
Ren Xi Zhou?
